 "<p>Pair-wise positional biases <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span> </p>\n": "<p>\u30da\u30a2\u30ef\u30a4\u30ba\u306e\u4f4d\u7f6e\u30d0\u30a4\u30a2\u30b9 <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span></p>\n",
 "<p>The denominator part <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span> </p>\n": "<p>\u5206\u6bcd\u90e8\u5206 <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span></p>\n",
 "<p>The numerator part <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span> </p>\n": "<p>\u5206\u5b50\u90e8\u5206 <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span></p>\n",
 "<p>These transform the <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span>, <span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span> and <span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span> vectors. </p>\n": "<p>\u3053\u308c\u3089\u306f<span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span>\u3001\u3001<span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span><span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span>\u304a\u3088\u3073\u30d9\u30af\u30c8\u30eb\u3092\u5909\u63db\u3057\u307e\u3059\u3002</p>\n",
 "<p>Transform query, key and value embeddings </p>\n": "<p>\u30af\u30a8\u30ea\u3001\u30ad\u30fc\u3001\u5024\u306e\u57cb\u3081\u8fbc\u307f\u3092\u5909\u63db</p>\n",
 "<p>We subtract <span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span> and <span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span> before calculating the exponents to stabilize the softmax calculation.</p>\n<p>If <span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span> is large <span translate=no>_^_3_^_</span> becomes huge and the computation of <span translate=no>_^_4_^_</span>becomes unstable. Subtracting a constant before calculating the exponent from numerator and denominator will cancel out. and can help stabilize the computation. So we subtract <span translate=no>_^_5_^_</span> to stabilize the computation. </p>\n": "<p>\u30bd\u30d5\u30c8\u30de\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u306e\u8a08\u7b97\u3092\u5b89\u5b9a\u3055\u305b\u308b\u305f\u3081\u306b\u3001<span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span><span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span>\u6307\u6570\u3092\u8a08\u7b97\u3059\u308b\u524d\u306b\u6e1b\u7b97\u3057\u307e\u3059\u3002</p>\n<p><span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span><span translate=no>_^_3_^_</span>\u5927\u304d\u3044\u3068\u5de8\u5927\u306b\u306a\u308a\u3001<span translate=no>_^_4_^_</span>\u306e\u8a08\u7b97\u304c\u4e0d\u5b89\u5b9a\u306b\u306a\u308a\u307e\u3059\u3002\u5206\u5b50\u3068\u5206\u6bcd\u304b\u3089\u6307\u6570\u3092\u8a08\u7b97\u3059\u308b\u524d\u306b\u5b9a\u6570\u3092\u5f15\u304f\u3068\u76f8\u6bba\u3055\u308c\u3001\u8a08\u7b97\u3092\u5b89\u5b9a\u3055\u305b\u308b\u306e\u306b\u5f79\u7acb\u3061\u307e\u3059\u3002\u305d\u3053\u3067\u3001<span translate=no>_^_5_^_</span>\u6e1b\u7b97\u3057\u3066\u8a08\u7b97\u3092\u5b89\u5b9a\u3055\u305b\u307e\u3059\u3002</p>\n",
 "<span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span><p>We compute <span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span>, <span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span> and <span translate=no>_^_3_^_</span> separately and do a matrix multiplication. We use einsum for clarity. </p>\n": "<span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span><p><span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span>\u8a08\u7b97\u3057<span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span>\u3001<span translate=no>_^_3_^_</span>\u5225\u3005\u306b\u884c\u5217\u306e\u4e57\u7b97\u3092\u884c\u3044\u307e\u3059\u3002\u308f\u304b\u308a\u3084\u3059\u304f\u3059\u308b\u305f\u3081\u306b\u30a2\u30a4\u30f3\u30b5\u30e0\u3092\u4f7f\u7528\u3057\u3066\u3044\u307e\u3059\u3002</p>\n",
 "<ul><li><span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span> is the number of features in the <span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span>, <span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span> and <span translate=no>_^_3_^_</span> vectors. </li>\n<li><span translate=no>_^_4_^_</span> is <span translate=no>_^_5_^_</span> </li>\n<li><span translate=no>_^_6_^_</span> is the local window size <span translate=no>_^_7_^_</span> </li>\n<li><span translate=no>_^_8_^_</span> is whether to have a bias parameter for transformations for <span translate=no>_^_9_^_</span>, <span translate=no>_^_10_^_</span> and <span translate=no>_^_11_^_</span>.</li></ul>\n": "<ul><li><span translate=no>_^_0_^_</span>\u306f<span translate=no>_^_1_^_</span>\u3001<span translate=no>_^_2_^_</span><span translate=no>_^_3_^_</span>\u304a\u3088\u3073\u30d9\u30af\u30c8\u30eb\u5185\u306e\u7279\u5fb4\u306e\u6570\u3067\u3059\u3002</li>\n<li><span translate=no>_^_4_^_</span>\u306f <span translate=no>_^_5_^_</span></li>\n<li><span translate=no>_^_6_^_</span>\u306f\u30ed\u30fc\u30ab\u30eb\u30a6\u30a3\u30f3\u30c9\u30a6\u30b5\u30a4\u30ba\u3067\u3059 <span translate=no>_^_7_^_</span></li>\n</ul><li><span translate=no>_^_8_^_</span>\u3001\u306e\u5909\u63db\u306b\u30d0\u30a4\u30a2\u30b9\u30d1\u30e9\u30e1\u30fc\u30bf\u3092\u8a2d\u5b9a\u3059\u308b\u304b\u3069\u3046\u304b\u3067\u3059\u3002<span translate=no>_^_9_^_</span> <span translate=no>_^_10_^_</span> <span translate=no>_^_11_^_</span></li>\n",
